Package com.BranchPackage

Class BranchSystem

java.lang.Object
com.BranchPackage.BranchSystem
public class BranchSystem extends Object
The BranchSystem class represents the system of a branch, including menu management and order processing.

      public ArrayList<FoodItem> Get_Customer_Menu()

    • Branch_Menu_Management

      public void Branch_Menu_Management()

    • addOrder

      public void addOrder(Order order)
      Adds an order to the list of new orders.
      Parameters:
      order - The order to be added.

    • collectOrder

      public void collectOrder(int orderId)
      Collects an order based on its ID, moving it from the ready to pick up list to the completed order list. Prints a message indicating the success or failure of the collection process.
      Parameters:
      orderId - The ID of the order to be collected.

    • View_New_Order

      public void View_New_Order()
      Displays the new orders by iterating through the new order list and calling DisplayOrder on each order.

    • Process_Order

      public void Process_Order()
      Processes new orders by displaying them, prompting the user to select an order for processing, and changing the order status to "Ready to Pick up" upon successful processing. Prints messages to inform the user about the process and handles input validation.

    • checkUncollectedOrders

      public void checkUncollectedOrders()
      Checks for uncollected orders beyond their collection deadline in the ready to pick up order list. If an order is beyond the deadline, it is removed from the ready to pick up list and added to the cancelled order list. Prints a message for each cancelled order.

    • getMenu

      public Menu getMenu()
      Retrieves the current menu associated with this branch system.
      Returns:
      The current menu.

    • setMenu

      public void setMenu(Menu menu)
      Sets the menu for this branch system.
      Parameters:
      menu - The menu to be set.
